bbq sauce
via http://www.cooks.com/recipe/qk78j7mq/homemade-bbq-sauce.html

Ingredients:

1/4 cup homemade enchilada sauce
2-3 tbsp brown sugar
1 tsp molasses (or bourbon syrup)
2 tsp smoked salt
1/4 cup apple cider vinegar
1 tsp mustard

combine all ingredients in a sauce pan on medium heat for 5 minutes until sugars dissolve and thicken.